title: On The 10th Year, The Transferee Who Gave Up Returning Finally Becomes The Protagonist - Novel Updates
genre: Action   Adventure   Drama   Fantasy   Harem   Seinen
tags: Adventurers   Demi-Humans   Elves   Fantasy World   Guilds   Magic   Magical Technology   Male Protagonist   Polygamy   Protagonist Strong from the Start   Transported to Another World   Twins   Unique Weapon User

description:
On the 10th year after his transfer.

It was more than enough time to awaken from what at first, felt like an exciting fantasy dream world.

And one this 10th year, the protagonist, Tor(Toru Wakusari), gives up searching for a way to return to Japan, after being successful for so long.

It was then that a job offer found its way to him—it was to be the bodyguard of twins who have knowledge of Earth.>
